data.description: Welcome to this charming and cozy 2300+/- sqft home featuring 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms with a bonus room above the garage, sitting on 1.66+/- acres in highly sought-after Coweta County! From the moment you step inside, you'll be greeted by a warm and inviting ambiance that's perfect for creating lasting memories. The spacious living room is designed to accommodate both relaxation and entertainment, providing the ideal backdrop for gatherings and social occasions! Step into the gourmet kitchen complete with granite countertops, tile backsplash, a pantry, and a breakfast area and bar. Whether you want to unwind with a good book or simply enjoy some quiet moments, the additional family room is the perfect spot. Step into the bright master bedroom with tray ceilings and an additional sitting area. This stunning home features a master bath that is sure to impress. The double sinks provide convenience and ample space, while the shower and separate soaking tub both offer a refreshing experience. Spacious walk-in closet, providing plenty of storage and organization for your wardrobe and accessories. The other well-appointed bedrooms offer comfortable retreats, while the bathroom ensures convenience and functionality for the household. This amazing home also comes with a 568 +/- sq ft detached garage, offering a blank canvas to bring your dreams to life! Imagine the possibilities - whether you envision a spacious entertainment area, a home gym, a workshop, or additional living space, this detached garage provides the foundation for your creative ideas. This home is a true gem, combining comfort and style. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this delightful space your own. Call The Charles Davis Team today to get more information or schedule a showing!
